<div class="title">Heaven and Hell</div>
<div class="substance">2C-T-2</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Stamfrog&Exact=1">Stamfrog</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Stamfrog. "Heaven and Hell: An Experience with 2C-T-2 (exp24903)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 26, 2008. erowid.org/exp/24903</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
